    "en": "The Messenger of God (peace be upon him and his family) led the people in Dhuhr and Asr prayers when the sun began to decline, in congregation, without any reason; and he led them in Maghrib and the last Isha prayer before the disappearance of the twilight, without any reason, in congregation. And the Messenger of God (peace be upon him and his family) did this only so that the time might be expanded for his community.",
